Currently we load properties for various things like i18n strings. These are simply loaded from the first .properties file in the classpath. I propose that instead of this we should load all the appropriate properties files using Enumeration<URL> getResources(String), and merge them together in classpath order. This would allow support or customers to override specific values by dropping their own overrides into WEB-INF/classes, instead of having to unjar/modify/jar/repeat-upon-upgrade which is currently required.

